Package domain.game_world

Class GameWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.game_world.GameWorld
  • public class GameWorld
extends java.lang.Object
    A class of gameWorlds, containing the grid, robot and startRobot. The startrobot is used to reset the game world.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      GameWorld()
      Initialize an empty game world with the standard grid and the robot at (0,0).
      GameWorld​(int width, int height)
      Initialize a gameworld with the given width and height.
      GameWorld​(domain.game_world.Grid grid, domain.game_world.Vector startPosition)
      Initialize a new gameworld with a given grid and height.
